                    <msContents>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <locus from="2ra" to="86ra"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT2505Weddas"/>
                            <note><bibl><ptr target="bm:Loefgren1974Katalog"/><citedRange unit="page">43–44</citedRange></bibl>
                                provides a general introduction to the work.
                            </note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                <hi rend="rubric">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡</hi> ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ 
                                <hi rend="rubric">አሐዱ፡ አምላክ። ን</hi>ወጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ 
                                እ<hi rend="rubric">ግዚአብሔር፡ ጽሒ</hi>ፈ፡ ስእለት፡ ወአስተብቍዖት፡
                                እንተ፡ ነበበ፡ ባቲ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ባስልዮስ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ዘቂሳርያ<hi rend="partialRubric">፨</hi>
                                በእንተ፡ ሰብዓቱ፡ ዕለታት፡ ዘመፍትው፡ ይጸልዩ፡ ባቲ፡ ለለ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዕለት<hi rend="partialRubric">፨</hi>
                                ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ ለአቡነ፡ ባስልዮስ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ፍቁሩ፡ 
                                <subst><del>
                                    <subst><del>
                                        <subst><del rend="erasure"/>
                                        <add place="overstrike"><hi rend="rubric">ታ<gap reason="illegible" unit="chars" quantity="4"/>ማኖት።</hi></add></subst>
                                    </del><add place="overstrike"><del rend="strikethrough"></del></add></subst>
                                </del>
                                    <add place="above">አዛርያስ፡</add></subst>
                                ለ<hi rend="rubric">ዓለመ፡ ዓለም። አሜን፡</hi>
                            </incipit>
                            <incipit>
                                <hi rend="rubric">ቀዳሜ፡ ስእለት፡፡ ዘይ</hi>ትነበብ፡ በዕለተ፡ ሰኑይ<hi rend="partialRubric">፨</hi>
                                ኦእግዚአብሔር፡ እግዚእየ፡ ሰራዬ፡ ኃጢአትየ፡ 
                                አ<cb n="b"/><hi rend="rubric">ንተ፡ ተአምር፡ ኵሎ፡ 
                                    <subst><del rend="erasure"/><add place="overstrike">ኃጢአተ፡ እ</add></subst></hi>ንተ፡ 
                                ገበር<hi rend="rubric">ክዋ፡ ጽሚተ። አንተ፡</hi> ውእቱ፡ ዘተአምር፡ 
                                <hi rend="rubric">ውሣጥያተ፡ ወትፈት</hi>ን፡ ልበ፡ ወኵልያተ<hi rend="partialRubric">፤</hi>
                            </incipit>
                            
                            
                            
                            
                            
                            
                            
                            
                            
                            
                            
                            
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                                <locus from="1ra" to="13ra"/>
                                <title type="complete">Part 1: Questions 1–16 with answers</title>
                                <note><bibl><ptr target="bm:Loefgren1974Katalog"/><citedRange unit="page">105</citedRange></bibl>
                                    cites the incipit. He
                                    notes that the colophon of this part (on <locus target="#13ra"/>) mentions that forty questions are missing from
                                    the beginning (<foreign xml:lang="gez">እምቀዳሚሁ፡</foreign>), concluding that the text has been
                                    abbreviated.
                                </note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    በእንተ፡ ዘከመ፡ ይኄይስ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ብሕትውና፡ እምሥርዓተ፡ ማኅበር<hi rend="partialRubric">፨</hi>
                                    <hi rend="rubric">ክፍል፡</hi> <hi rend="partialRubric">፩</hi>ይቤሉ፡ 
                                    አኃው፡ ንወጥን፡ እምጥንቱ፡ ለግብር፡ ሀለዉ፡ ክልኤቱ፡ አኃው፡ 
                                    ወልደ፡ ብእሲ፡ ነጋዲ፡ ወሶበ፡ አዕረፈ፡ አባሆሙ፡ ወተካፈሉ፡ ርስቶ፡
                                </incipit>
                                <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ወይደሉ፡ እንከ፡ ለነ፡ ከመ፡ ንእመን፡ ዘይትበሀል፡ በእንተ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ እምዜናውያን፡ 
                                    ጽዱቃውያን<hi rend="partialRubric">፨</hi> ወለእመኒ፡ ኢሀለዉ፡ በአዝማኒነ፡ 
                                </explicit>
                                <explicit type="colophon" xml:lang="gez">
                                    <locus target="#13ra"/>
                                    ተፈጸመ፡ ክፍል፡ ቀዳሚ፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወነገረ፡ ከመ፡ ተኃጥአ፡ እምቀዳሚሁ፡ 
                                    <hi rend="partialRubric">፵</hi>ተስእሎታት<hi rend="partialRubric">፨</hi>
                                </explicit>
                            </msItem>
                            
                            
